// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1972 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 1aa3588f-e330-5a5f-b276-efc50ab3b54b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*")
